00:57:34.940 --> 00:57:38.250 align:middle line:10%
then the darkness
is what illuminates,

00:57:38.250 --> 00:57:39.669 align:middle line:10%
that gives the opportunity--

00:57:39.669 --> 00:57:41.210 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: The contrast
for the light.

00:57:41.210 --> 00:57:43.100 align:middle line:10%
>>PERRON: --for the light.

00:57:43.100 --> 00:57:45.560 align:middle line:10%
And they don't judge
in the way that we do.

00:57:45.560 --> 00:57:47.000 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: No, I know that.

00:57:47.000 --> 00:57:49.550 align:middle line:84%
>>PERRON: They observe
more than anything.

00:57:49.550 --> 00:57:53.900 align:middle line:84%
And they understand that we are
an incredibly self-destructive

00:57:53.900 --> 00:57:57.570 align:middle line:84%
race, that we rising
out of that now.

00:57:57.570 --> 00:57:59.930 align:middle line:84%
And that there are
those, on the planet,

00:57:59.930 --> 00:58:03.860 align:middle line:84%
among us, yourself, myself,
and myriad other people,

00:58:03.860 --> 00:58:06.170 align:middle line:84%
who are saying the
same thing that's

00:58:06.170 --> 00:58:08.960 align:middle line:84%
been said for
millennia by teachers

00:58:08.960 --> 00:58:11.600 align:middle line:90%
that have come and gone.

00:58:11.600 --> 00:58:14.510 align:middle line:84%
But people are listening
in a different way now.

00:58:14.510 --> 00:58:19.200 align:middle line:84%
The message is resonating in
ways that it hasn't before.

00:58:19.200 --> 00:58:23.330 align:middle line:84%
And one of my theories, and
the things that I work on most,

00:58:23.330 --> 00:58:27.430 align:middle line:84%
is my absolute knowledge
that thoughts are things.

00:58:27.430 --> 00:58:30.590 align:middle line:84%
And that we can literally
heal this planet

00:58:30.590 --> 00:58:33.470 align:middle line:84%
and ourselves with our
own thought process.

00:58:33.470 --> 00:58:36.880 align:middle line:84%
Everything comes from
within and so without.

00:58:36.880 --> 00:58:39.740 align:middle line:84%
And I truly believe that
there is a creative source,

00:58:39.740 --> 00:58:41.570 align:middle line:90%
that there is a prime creator.

00:58:41.570 --> 00:58:44.270 align:middle line:84%
And interestingly, a number
of the different races

00:58:44.270 --> 00:58:48.290 align:middle line:84%
that routinely visit this planet
believe the same thing, where

00:58:48.290 --> 00:58:50.270 align:middle line:90%
many are humanoid.

00:58:50.270 --> 00:58:54.950 align:middle line:84%
So they have grappled with the
same questions of existence

00:58:54.950 --> 00:58:56.300 align:middle line:90%
that we have.

00:58:56.300 --> 00:58:59.690 align:middle line:84%
And they're called
the light beings

00:58:59.690 --> 00:59:02.090 align:middle line:90%
in the spiritual community.

00:59:02.090 --> 00:59:04.700 align:middle line:84%
There's a whole new
vernacular for this.

00:59:04.700 --> 00:59:08.060 align:middle line:84%
I tend not to label anything,
because, if everything

00:59:08.060 --> 00:59:10.460 align:middle line:84%
is one thing, then,
really, what we're doing

00:59:10.460 --> 00:59:17.870 align:middle line:84%
is we're exploring the
incredible equation

00:59:17.870 --> 00:59:19.070 align:middle line:90%
of existence.

00:59:19.070 --> 00:59:21.350 align:middle line:84%
I personally believe
that everything

00:59:21.350 --> 00:59:23.350 align:middle line:90%
that we perceive to be magical--

00:59:23.350 --> 00:59:24.320 align:middle line:90%
and I love that word.

00:59:24.320 --> 00:59:25.590 align:middle line:90%
I use it all the time--

00:59:25.590 --> 00:59:28.760 align:middle line:84%
but it's just science
we don't understand yet.

00:59:28.760 --> 00:59:30.892 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:59:30.892 --> 00:59:33.830 align:middle line:84%
>>PERRON: My research is
basically experiential.

00:59:33.830 --> 00:59:35.040 align:middle line:90%
I invite it.

00:59:35.040 --> 00:59:35.840 align:middle line:90%
I go out.

00:59:35.840 --> 00:59:37.460 align:middle line:90%
I sing to them.

00:59:37.460 --> 00:59:39.030 align:middle line:90%
It's all consciousness-based.

00:59:39.030 --> 00:59:39.830 align:middle line:90%
And I sing to them.

00:59:39.830 --> 00:59:41.750 align:middle line:90%
And I talk to them aloud.

00:59:41.750 --> 00:59:44.420 align:middle line:84%
My father has had
many experiences.

00:59:44.420 --> 00:59:46.520 align:middle line:90%
Everyone in my family has.

00:59:46.520 --> 00:59:47.880 align:middle line:90%
Some won't talk about it.

00:59:47.880 --> 00:59:49.520 align:middle line:90%
My father is very open about it.

00:59:49.520 --> 00:59:51.920 align:middle line:90%
My mother is very open about it.

00:59:51.920 --> 00:59:54.320 align:middle line:84%
In fact, I was visiting
her a few weeks ago.

00:59:54.320 --> 00:59:57.390 align:middle line:84%
And I said, mom, oh, there's
a great vessel out here.

00:59:57.390 --> 00:59:58.190 align:middle line:90%
Come on.

00:59:58.190 --> 00:59:58.990 align:middle line:90%
Come on.

00:59:58.990 --> 01:00:01.268 align:middle line:84%
She's like, oh,
honey, you go ahead.

01:00:01.268 --> 01:00:02.216 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Been there.

01:00:02.216 --> 01:00:04.361 align:middle line:90%
I'm finishing making a cake.

01:00:04.361 --> 01:00:06.610 align:middle line:84%
>>PERRON: Let me finish my
coffee, then I'll come out.

01:00:06.610 --> 01:00:07.776 align:middle line:90%
If they're still there, yay.

01:00:07.776 --> 01:00:10.370 align:middle line:90%


01:00:10.370 --> 01:00:14.370 align:middle line:84%
I guess we're paranormal
in that respect.

01:00:14.370 --> 01:00:17.530 align:middle line:90%
But a lot of people are.

01:00:17.530 --> 01:00:20.090 align:middle line:84%
There are those that
see multi-dimensionally,

01:00:20.090 --> 01:00:21.920 align:middle line:84%
extra-dimensionally,
on the planet.

01:00:21.920 --> 01:00:25.270 align:middle line:84%
I think we're
most-likely hybrid DNA,

01:00:25.270 --> 01:00:27.940 align:middle line:84%
blue-eyed, green-eyed
people, Rh negative.

01:00:27.940 --> 01:00:30.070 align:middle line:84%
I think that the
science is coming around

01:00:30.070 --> 01:00:31.810 align:middle line:90%
to validate some of that.

01:00:31.810 --> 01:00:34.180 align:middle line:84%
But really, my job
on the planet is

01:00:34.180 --> 01:00:36.580 align:middle line:84%
to raise the vibration
of the planet,

01:00:36.580 --> 01:00:38.980 align:middle line:84%
to heighten the
frequency, to bring people

01:00:38.980 --> 01:00:41.590 align:middle line:84%
into the notion and
the understanding

01:00:41.590 --> 01:00:45.490 align:middle line:84%
that there is a logical
way that we can literally

01:00:45.490 --> 01:00:48.280 align:middle line:84%
change the world through
our own thought process.

01:00:48.280 --> 01:00:50.020 align:middle line:90%
And it's very specific.

01:00:50.020 --> 01:00:53.200 align:middle line:84%
And when we are bombarded
with negative energy

01:00:53.200 --> 01:00:55.865 align:middle line:84%
and negative stimuli, clear
that out of your mind.

01:00:55.865 --> 01:00:56.740 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: No kidding.

01:00:56.740 --> 01:00:58.210 align:middle line:84%
>>PERRON: You can
have the choice.

01:00:58.210 --> 01:01:00.700 align:middle line:84%
You make the choice
every moment of your life

01:01:00.700 --> 01:01:02.680 align:middle line:84%
how you are going
to live your life.

01:01:02.680 --> 01:01:04.820 align:middle line:84%
And if you clear
that, and you create

01:01:04.820 --> 01:01:08.110 align:middle line:84%
a void and a vacancy in your
consciousness, you must,

01:01:08.110 --> 01:01:11.650 align:middle line:84%
absolutely must,
immediately fill that void

01:01:11.650 --> 01:01:16.300 align:middle line:84%
or whatever it was that was
negative, that you expelled,

01:01:16.300 --> 01:01:20.350 align:middle line:84%
will slowly and insidiously
refill that void.

01:01:20.350 --> 01:01:22.247 align:middle line:84%
You have to fill
the void, yourself.

01:01:22.247 --> 01:01:23.080 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: By choice.

01:01:23.080 --> 01:01:23.755 align:middle line:90%
>>PERRON: By choice.

01:01:23.755 --> 01:01:24.190 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I agree with you.

01:01:24.190 --> 01:01:26.260 align:middle line:84%
>>PERRON: And that's
why I say, I have seen

01:01:26.260 --> 01:01:27.910 align:middle line:90%
the dark side of existence.

01:01:27.910 --> 01:01:31.810 align:middle line:84%
I deliberately choose
to live in the light.

01:01:31.810 --> 01:01:33.430 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: On that, OK.

